reviewText: The first two are really funny and delightful to watch.  The third one has funny moments, but it is obvious that it is weaker than the first two.  Would I recommend all three?  Absolutely!  And they look fantastic on blu-ray.  They couldn't have picked better actors to play Greg, Rodrick, Susan the mother, and Fregley, the redhead.  They nailed it.  Super highly recommended.
